data.description: Introducing this stunning waterfront home, a true gem nestled along the North River. With its deep water access and proximity to the Intracoastal Waterway, Cumberland Island, and the Atlantic Ocean, this property offers an unparalleled coastal living experience. As you step into the backyard, you'll be greeted by a floating dock measuring 36'x8', equipped with power and water connections. This is the perfect spot to moor your yacht and embark on your aquatic adventures. Additionally, there is a spacious upper dock measuring 24'x24', complete with a convenient fish cleaning station, ideal for those who enjoy fishing or entertaining by the water. The outdoor amenities continue with an inground enclosed pool and patio area, providing a private oasis to relax and soak up the sun. Imagine lounging by the pool, surrounded by mature oak trees, and enjoying breathtaking sunset views over the North River. Inside the home, you'll find a meticulously updated interior with new appliances, ensuring a modern and comfortable living experience. The open floor plan allows for seamless flow between the living spaces, creating an inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment. This home is located on a cul de sac with additional features including an inground sprinkler system, a workshop with power for all your DIY projects, and the rare advantage of no homeowners association (HOA) fees. One of the most remarkable aspects of this property is the deep water access it offers even at low tide. This means you can navigate your vessel from your own dock to the ocean with ease. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this unique waterfront home your forever home. Schedule a viewing today and let the tranquil waters and coastal charm capture your heart"
